      "releaseNotes": "Glasses Home has a fresh, cleaner design that makes everything easier to find and control.\n• See your glasses status at a glance with an improved glasses home screen.\n• Quickly access sessions like live translation and  modes like do not disturb in a redesigned Control Center.\n• Keep controls for active features — like navigation or live translation — visible as you navigate between tabs.\n\n*Certain Meta AI features are only available in select countries and languages. Some of these features may roll out slowly over time.",
